data.description: Executive Style West Palmdale Home with almost 4,000 sq. ft., Enjoy a cup of coffee on the quaint porch area.  Once you enter the foyer there's an office to your left and a nook/tea room to your right.  Step down into the formal living and dining room with a fireplace and wood/laminate flooring. To the right is a large family room with plantation shutters and fireplace. Enjoy entertaining in your gourmet kitchen w/granite counter tops and double islands. Head upstairs to an elegant double door master suite with wood laminate flooring.  Master bathroom offers a separate tub and shower w/double sinks and an oversize master walk in closet w/built in cabinets. Enjoy a large entertainment/bonus room with a small kitchenette and fireplace. An entertainers backyard is a must see with a covered patio, waterfall, and so much more! This home currently a 3 bedroom but could be a 5 or 6 bedroom home . Too many upgrades to mention this a ''Must See'' home!
